# PE_INT Scope Boundary

When working on PE_INT tasks, do not modify files outside `designs/PE_INT/`
unless the user explicitly confirms that cross-tree change first.

If a PE_INT issue appears to require PyCircuit framework changes, stop and ask
the user whether to:

- file or update a framework issue,
- make a framework patch in the same branch, or
- keep the change documented as a known limitation.

This rule does not block read-only inspection outside `designs/PE_INT/`.
